episode of.title: Bug Juice: My Adventures at Camp (TV Series 2018– )

2.plot: The girls of Pines 4 eagerly await the arrival of two new cabin mates as the boys of Pines 9 help Darryl bounce back after a disappointing swim test.

episode of.title: Bug Juice: My Adventures at Camp (TV Series 2018– )

3.plot: The 4th of July at Wazi has the kids excited to take on new challenges. Vegas night tests friendships when Brynn decides to take a risk, dividing the cabin and testing friendships.

episode of.title: Bug Juice: My Adventures at Camp (TV Series 2018– )

4.plot: The cabins have new counselors and the kids feast on tacos for breakfast. At the evening event, the kids have their fortunes read and the counselors are soaked in a dunk tank.

episode of.title: Bug Juice: My Adventures at Camp (TV Series 2018– )

5.plot: There's a zombie breakout and the power of friendship is the only defense! The campers are tested in an epic game of tag. An underground candy trade has the camp buzzing.

episode of.title: Bug Juice: My Adventures at Camp (TV Series 2018– )

8.plot: The girls celebrate the end of Session 1 with a rolling competition, while some of the boys tackle their fears at the waterfront. All of Wazi comes together for a special campfire.

episode of.title: Bug Juice: My Adventures at Camp (TV Series 2018– )

episode of.title: Bug Juice: My Adventures at Camp (TV Series 2018– )

11.plot: Lucy faces a 50-foot climbing wall, blindfolded and one legged; a taco of terror scares no one; Halloween in summer is a night of fright.

episode of.title: Bug Juice: My Adventures at Camp (TV Series 2018– )

12.plot: Andrew gets Doggy, Izzy gets Hare-y and Aaralyn gets grape-y for the final play of the summer; the Untalent show highlights the bizarre talents of the campers.

episode of.title: Bug Juice: My Adventures at Camp (TV Series 2018– )

13.plot: Wazi Casino opens its doors for card games and weddings, with Leo getting nicknamed the wedding bandit; Alex and Andrew take to the lake to reach their goals.

15.plot: The Parker Cup, an epic two-day competition, divides the camp and tests friendships; the kids battle it out in a camp-wide relay race, a sky-high egg-drop, and a penalty kick round of soccer.

16.title: Best Summer Ever!

episode of.title: Bug Juice: My Adventures at Camp (TV Series 2018– )

16.plot: As summer draws to a close, campers participate in a Wazi-wide dodge ball game; the campers dress up for a fancy banquet before saying their goodbyes and heading back home.

imdb.title: Bug Juice: My Adventures at Camp
akas: Bug Juice: My Adventures at Camp (United States)
plot: Chronicles the outdoor fun, team activities, new friendships and the experience of being away from home for a new generation of kids at the popular Camp Waziyatah in Waterford, Maine.
